Change record CHG-2026-4471 has been approved and implemented.

TICKET SUMMARY
--------------
Change type: venue and schedule reconfiguration
Event: Maplewood Educational Leadership Conference
Session: Keynote presentation by Mary Vasquez, Principal Ridgewood Collegiate
Original scheduled slot: 14:15 with 45 minute session length preceded by
panel discussion at 13:30 to 14:15
Approved change: consolidate slot to 14:00 with 60 minute session length,
the preceding panel discussion has been folded into the same slot on the
speaker's presentation and there will be no separate pre-panel presenter

Original venue: Cordell Hall, main floor east wing capacity 480 seats
Approved venue: Theatre B, lower level north wing capacity 320 seats

Reason for change: Cordell Hall electrical service work was extended by
the facilities contractor beyond the original completion window. Theatre B
is the closest venue with the audio visual capability the session requires.
The audio visual walkthrough for Theatre B has been booked for 12:30 the
day of the event, one hour before session start.

CATERING AND SIGNAGE
--------------------
Signage at Cordell Hall entrance will redirect attendees to Theatre B.
Water and coffee service moved to the Theatre B foyer. Session sign in
sheets have been reprinted with the new venue and time.

RECORDING NOTES
---------------
Theatre B has a fixed camera position that the recording team confirmed
covers the stage lectern and the projection screen. The recording will
be uploaded to the conference video host within seven business days of
the session end. The speaker retains editorial approval before the file
is published to any wider audience.

